The Firm also offers advisory, investment banking and capital raising services to its clients.
Prior to starting his own firm, Omeed was a Managing Director and the Global Head of the Hedge Fund Advisory Business at Bank of America Merrill Lynch.
Omeed was also the founder and head of the Emerging Manager Program within the Global Equities business.
Omeed is a Term Member of the Council on Foreign Relations, a Centennial Society Member of the Economic Club of New York and a Chairman’s Circle Member of the Milken Institute.”